pyBotMiner is a Minecraft Bot (development in progress).

The aim is to interact with a user by using the chat command line.

Packages needed:
Twister : for the protocol implementation
Zope.Interface : for Twister
numpy : To store the Map and compute vectors


Currently:
- Protocol completed : Bot is alive
- Command are entered in the chat line. 
	The format is: BotName command   (ex: bot lookat me)


Existing Commands (case insensitive):
Lookat me (or l)   - the bot is looking to you
Jump (or j)        - small jump just for a test
Quit (or q)        - quit :-)




